            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel your <strong>mango[es]</strong></p><p>Stand the <strong>mango[es]</strong> upright and very carefully slice the flesh away from the stone</p><p>Tip: If you feel resistance against your knife, it means you are hitting the stone!</p><p>Dice the <strong>mango flesh</strong> finely, discarding the stone[s]</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684497867487-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684497867487-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
