          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1684497875882-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped mint</strong> with the <strong>remaining diced mango</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>remaining chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>mango & mint</strong></p><p>Once the dal is ready, wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then add it to the pan and give everything a good mix up until the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>coconut & mango dal</strong></p><p>Fluff the<strong> basmati rice</strong> with a fork</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1684497878444-x200.jpg",
