            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>coconut & mango dal </strong>with the<strong> fluffy rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a bowl and turn out</p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and top with the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>mango & mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
